Usage: deriveTimingBudget [-help] [-parameterized] [-views <string>] [-cycleRatio | -stageBased ] [-inst <string> | -ptn <string> | -allIlmHinsts ] [ -verbose ]

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
-allIlmHinsts                    # allIlmHinsts (bool, optional)
-cycleRatio                      # cycleRatio (bool, optional)
-inst <string>                   # inst (string, optional)
-parameterized                   # use parameterized clock period in ptn
                                 # constraints (bool, optional)
-ptn <string>                    # ptn (string, optional)
-stageBased                      # Staged based Budgeting (bool, optional)
-verbose                         # Verbose option for various controls
                                 # (bool, optional)
-views <string>                  # views (string, optional)